\[
\| egin{pmatrix} 4 \ -18 \ -4 \end{pmatrix}\| = \sqrt{4^2 + (-18)^2 + (-4)^2} = \sqrt{16 + 324 + 16} = \sqrt{356} = 2\sqrt {89}.
\]

最后，距离 \(D\) 是：
\[
D =  rac{2\sqrt{4361}}{2\sqrt{89}} =  rac{\sqrt{4361}}{\sqrt{89}} = \sqrt{ rac{4361}{89}} = \sqrt{49} = 7.
\]

